<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Abdoul Kane - Part Service Designer, Part Developer</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v6.1.2/css/all.css">


</head>
<body>


<div class="wrapper clearfix wrapper_padding "> <!-- Move the wrapper inside the body and correct the class -->
  <div class="col-1 about homepage_content"> <!-- Remove the dot before the class name -->
    <h2>About</h2>
    <hr>
    <p>I am service designer & developer living in Winterthur Switzerland.</p>
    <p>By day I work as a service designer at Medic, by night contribute on open source and personal design & code rails, javascript, html/css </p>
    <p>You can find me speaking on Twitter, swooshing some pixel on Dribbble, and sharing some code on Github.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
  <h2>Stuff I've Written</h2>
  <hr>
  <%  @posts.each do |post| %>
      <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
       <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %></a></h3>
  <% end %>

</div>
  <div class="col-3 homepage_content">
  <h2>Stuff I've Built</h2>
  <hr>
   <%  @projects.each do |project| %>
        <p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
       <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to project.title, project %></a></h3>
  <% end %>
  <hr>
  </div>
</div>



</body>

</html>
